    String C370111Contaminated_A = "(A) A FOOD that is unsafe, ADULTERATED, or not honestly presented as specified under Subpart 3-101.11 shall be discarded or reconditioned according to an APPROVED procedure. P";
    String C370111Contaminated_B = "(B) FOOD that is not from an APPROVED source as specified under Subpart 3-\n" +
            "201.11.17 shall be discarded. P";
